wiki.content:
This album is famous for being produced by the 19 year old Ry Cooder, and his influence - mainly the amazing slide guitar work throughout and especially on "Sure 'Nuff 'n' Yes, I Do" - was the template for his later solo work, as well as his guest work with the Stones and even early Little Feat.
